Name: LEOPARD syndrome 1
Definition: A LEOPARD syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the PTPN11 gene on chromosome 12q24.

Name: LEOPARD syndrome 2
Definition: A LEOPARD syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the RAF1 gene on chromosome 3p25.

Name: LEOPARD syndrome 3
Definition: A LEOPARD syndrome that has_material_basis_in heterozygous mutation in the BRAF gene on chromosome 7q34.
